---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Oasis Dental Care — Precision dentistry in Huntington Beach"
  description="Precision, technology-forward dentistry in Huntington Beach. Same-day crowns, 3D imaging, implants & Invisalign with Dr. Jason Fu. Call (714) 893-2106."
>

<!-- hero -->
<section class="hero reveal in">
  <div class="heromain">
    <div class="inner">
      <div class="copy">
        <span class="tag" style="font-size:15px">Precision dentistry · Huntington Beach</span>
        <h1>Modern dental care, <span>dialed&nbsp;in.</span></h1>
        <p>Same-day crowns, 3D imaging and gentle, technology-forward treatment — so your visit is safer, faster, and more precise. Led by Dr. Jason Fu.</p>
        <div class="acts">
          <a class="btn" href="/contact">Request appointment <svg class="ico" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg></a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="tel:7148932106">Call (714) 893-2106</a>
        </div>
        <div class="specs">
          <div class="sp"><div class="n">25+</div><div class="l">Years exp.</div></div>
          <div class="sp"><div class="n">5.0★</div><div class="l">Rated</div></div>
          <div class="sp"><div class="n">Same-day</div><div class="l">Emergencies</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="media">
        <div class="ph">
          <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="5" width="18" height="14" rx="2"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="10" r="1.6"/><path d="m21 16-4.5-4.5L7 21"/></svg></div>
          <div class="t">Team photo</div>
          <div class="s">Placeholder — drop in your real team photos after the shoot.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="badge" style="font-size:12px"><span class="pulse" style="width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--teal-300)"></span>Our Team</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- marquee -->
<div class="strip">
  <div class="track">
    <span><b>+</b> General Dentistry <b>+</b> Implants <b>+</b> Invisalign® <b>+</b> Cosmetic <b>+</b> Same-Day Crowns <b>+</b> Emergency Care <b>+</b> Teeth Whitening <b>+</b> Root Canal <b>+</b> Pediatric <b>+</b> Veneers</span>
    <span><b>+</b> General Dentistry <b>+</b> Implants <b>+</b> Invisalign® <b>+</b> Cosmetic <b>+</b> Same-Day Crowns <b>+</b> Emergency Care <b>+</b> Teeth Whitening <b>+</b> Root Canal <b>+</b> Pediatric <b>+</b> Veneers</span>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- services bento -->
<section class="pad" id="services">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="shead reveal">
      <div><span class="tag">/ Services</span><h2>Every treatment, one system.</h2></div>
      <p>A full-service practice — from preventive visits to advanced restorative and cosmetic work, all under one roof in Huntington Beach.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bento reveal">
      <div class="cell teal wide">
        <div class="bgico" style="width:160px;height:160px;right:0;top:0"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 2C6.5 2 5 4.5 5 7c0 2.5.8 4.8 1.6 7.5L8 22h8l1.4-7.5C18.2 11.8 19 9.5 19 7c0-2.5-1.5-5-4-5-1 0-1.8.5-3 .5-1.2 0-2-.5-3-.5z"/></svg></div>
        <div class="ch"><span class="num">[01]</span></div>
        <div class="cb"><div><h3>General Dentistry</h3><p>Cleanings, exams and gentle checkups — the backbone of a healthy smile.</p></div><div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 2C6.5 2 5 4.5 5 7c0 2.5.8 4.8 1.6 7.5L8 22h8l1.4-7.5C18.2 11.8 19 9.5 19 7c0-2.5-1.5-5-4-5-1 0-1.8.5-3 .5-1.2 0-2-.5-3-.5z"/></svg></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="cell">
        <div class="bgico" style="width:130px;height:130px;right:0;top:0"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M10 3C8 3 7 5 7 7c0 2 .6 3.8 1.2 6L9.5 19h5L16 13c.6-2.2 1.2-4 1.2-6 0-2-1-4-3.2-4-1 0-1.5.4-2 .4S11 3 10 3z"/></svg></div>
        <div class="ch"><span class="num">[02]</span></div>
        <div class="cb"><div><h3>Cosmetic</h3><span class="arr">View →</span></div><div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M10 3C8 3 7 5 7 7c0 2 .6 3.8 1.2 6L9.5 19h5L16 13c.6-2.2 1.2-4 1.2-6 0-2-1-4-3.2-4-1 0-1.5.4-2 .4S11 3 10 3z"/></svg></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="cell">
        <div class="bgico" style="width:115px;height:115px;right:0;top:0"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2v7"/><rect x="9" y="9" width="6" height="3" rx="1"/><path d="M10.5 12l-1 8h5l-1-8"/><path d="M9.5 20h5"/></svg></div>
        <div class="ch"><span class="num">[03]</span></div>
        <div class="cb"><div><h3>Implants</h3><span class="arr">View →</span></div><div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2v7"/><rect x="9" y="9" width="6" height="3" rx="1"/><path d="M10.5 12l-1 8h5l-1-8"/><path d="M9.5 20h5"/></svg></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="cell dark feat tall">
        <div class="grid-ov"></div>
        <div class="bgico" style="width:148px;height:148px;right:0;top:0"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3 10c0-2.8 4-5 9-5s9 2.2 9 5v2a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/><path d="M7 14v2.5M12 14.5V18M17 14v2.5"/></svg></div>
        <div class="ch" style="position:relative"><span class="num">[04]</span></div>
        <div class="cb" style="position:relative"><div><h3>Invisalign®</h3><p>Nearly-invisible aligners with a precise digital treatment plan built around your lifestyle.</p><span class="arr" style="margin-top:12px">Start your scan →</span></div><div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3 10c0-2.8 4-5 9-5s9 2.2 9 5v2a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/><path d="M7 14v2.5M12 14.5V18M17 14v2.5"/></svg></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="cell">
        <div class="bgico" style="width:130px;height:130px;right:0;top:0"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3 20h18M5 20V10l3.5 4L12 3l3.5 11L19 10v10"/></svg></div>
        <div class="ch"><span class="num">[05]</span></div>
        <div class="cb"><div><h3>Crowns &amp; Bridges</h3><span class="arr">View →</span></div><div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3 20h18M5 20V10l3.5 4L12 3l3.5 11L19 10v10"/></svg></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="cell">
        <div class="bgico" style="width:122px;height:122px;right:0;top:0"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9.5 2C7 2 5.5 4 5.5 6.5c0 2.3.7 4.3 1.4 7L8 20h8l1.1-6.5c.7-2.7 1.4-4.7 1.4-7C18.5 4 17 2 14.5 2z"/></svg></div>
        <div class="ch"><span class="num">[06]</span></div>
        <div class="cb"><div><h3>Emergency</h3><span class="arr">Same-day →</span></div><div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9.5 2C7 2 5.5 4 5.5 6.5c0 2.3.7 4.3 1.4 7L8 20h8l1.1-6.5c.7-2.7 1.4-4.7 1.4-7C18.5 4 17 2 14.5 2z"/></svg></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="cell wide">
        <div class="bgico" style="width:155px;height:155px;right:0;top:0"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M10 3.5C8 3.5 7 5.5 7 7.5c0 2 .6 3.8 1.2 6L9.5 19h5L16 13.5c.6-2.2 1.2-4 1.2-6 0-2-1-4-3.2-4-1 0-1.5.5-2 .5S11 3.5 10 3.5z"/></svg></div>
        <div class="ch"><span class="num">[07]</span></div>
        <div class="cb"><div><h3>Teeth Whitening</h3><p>In-office and take-home options — refresh your smile on your schedule, no guesswork.</p></div><div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M10 3.5C8 3.5 7 5.5 7 7.5c0 2 .6 3.8 1.2 6L9.5 19h5L16 13.5c.6-2.2 1.2-4 1.2-6 0-2-1-4-3.2-4-1 0-1.5.5-2 .5S11 3.5 10 3.5z"/></svg></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-top:26px" class="reveal"><a class="btn btn-out" href="/services">View all 13 services <svg class="ico" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg></a></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- tech / difference -->
<section class="pad tech" id="difference">
  <div class="grid-ov"></div>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="shead reveal">
      <div><span class="tag">The Oasis difference</span><h2>Built around precision &amp; comfort.</h2></div>
      <p>It's not just the technology — it's how we listen, explain, and treat every patient like a neighbor.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="tgrid reveal">
      <div class="tcard"><div class="num">01 — Imaging</div><h3>Digital X-rays &amp; 3D</h3><p>Lower-dose digital imaging and 3D scans mean faster, safer, more accurate diagnosis.</p></div>
      <div class="tcard"><div class="num">02 — Restorative</div><h3>Same-day crowns</h3><p>In-house technology lets us complete many restorations in a single visit — no second trip.</p></div>
      <div class="tcard"><div class="num">03 — Safety</div><h3>ADA · CDC · OSHA</h3><p>Rigorous sterilization and infection-control protocols at the heart of everything we do.</p></div>
      <div class="tcard"><div class="num">04 — Comfort</div><h3>Comfort-driven design</h3><p>Sunlit rooms, calming colors and plush chairs built to help you relax from the moment you arrive.</p></div>
      <div class="tcard"><div class="num">05 — Scheduling</div><h3>On-time, every time</h3><p>A 2 p.m. cleaning means you're seated at 2 p.m. Your time matters as much as your smile.</p></div>
      <div class="tcard"><div class="num">06 — Community</div><h3>Rooted in Surf City</h3><p>Proud to serve Huntington Beach families, locals and weekend beachgoers alike.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- doctor -->
<section class="pad doc" id="doctor">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="pic reveal">
      <img src="https://oasisdentalcarehb.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Dr-Jason-Fu-2021.jpg" alt="Dr. Jason Fu" />
      <div class="ovl"><span class="nm">Dr. Jason Fu</span><span class="rl" style="font-size:15px">Lead Dentist</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="reveal">
      <span class="tag">/ Meet your dentist</span>
      <h2>Advanced expertise, a calm chairside manner.</h2>
      <p>Dr. Fu brings over 25 years of clinical experience to Oasis Dental Care, pairing advanced technique with a patient-focused approach. He takes the time to answer questions and walk you through every option — preventive, restorative or cosmetic.</p>
      <p>Together with Leandre and Edith, our office team, he's built a practice where clinical precision and genuine warmth go hand in hand.</p>
      <div class="meta">
        <div><div class="n">25+</div><div class="l">Years exp.</div></div>
        <div><div class="n">10k+</div><div class="l">Smiles cared for</div></div>
        <div><div class="n">5.0★</div><div class="l">Patient rated</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- reviews -->
<section class="pad rev" id="reviews">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="shead reveal">
      <div><span class="tag">Patient reviews</span><h2>5.0 average. Real people.</h2></div>
      <p>From first-timers to patients of a decade — here's the Huntington Beach community on Oasis.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rgrid reveal">
      <div class="rc"><div class="top"><span class="st">★★★★★</span><span class="src">Google</span></div><q>Everyone is friendly and professional. I always learn something new and get good advice.</q><div class="who">Robert W. · Since 2015</div></div>
      <div class="rc"><div class="top"><span class="st">★★★★★</span><span class="src">Yelp</span></div><q>They eased my nerves and made it far less scary. Clean, accurate and affordable work.</q><div class="who">Saga E. · Los Angeles</div></div>
      <div class="rc"><div class="top"><span class="st">★★★★★</span><span class="src">Google</span></div><q>This is the future of dentistry right here. Recommend ten times over.</q><div class="who">Michelle G. · Los Angeles</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- location -->
<section class="pad loc" id="location">
  <div class="wrap reveal">
    <div class="info">
      <span class="tag">Visit us</span>
      <h2>6552 Bolsa Ave, Suite J</h2>
      <div class="addr">Huntington Beach, CA 92647<br /><a href="tel:7148932106" style="color:var(--teal);font-weight:600">(714) 893-2106</a> · oasisdentalcarehb@yahoo.com</div>
      <div class="hours">
        <div class="hr"><span>Monday – Thursday</span><span>09:00 AM to 5:00 PM</span></div>
        <div class="hr"><span>Friday</span><span>09:00 AM to 4:00 PM</span></div>
        <div class="hr"><span>Saturday</span><span>By Appointment</span></div>
        <div class="hr c"><span>Sunday</span><span>Closed</span></div>
      </div>
      <div style="margin-top:24px;display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap">
        <a class="btn" href="https://maps.google.com/maps?q=6552%20Bolsa%20Ave%2C%20Suite%20J%20Huntington%20Beach%2C%20CA%2092647" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Directions</a>
        <a class="btn btn-out" href="/contact">Patient forms</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="map">
      <iframe loading="lazy" title="Map" src="https://maps.google.com/maps?q=6552%20Bolsa%20Ave%2C%20Suite%20J%20Huntington%20Beach%2C%20CA%2092647&t=m&z=15&output=embed&iwloc=near"></iframe>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- book -->
<section class="book" id="book">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="bookcard reveal">
      <div class="grid-ov"></div>
      <div class="c">
        <span class="tag" style="font-size:15px">New patients welcome</span>
        <h2>Ready when you are.</h2>
        <p>Tell us a good time and someone warm will get back to you — usually the same day.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="acts">
        <a class="btn" href="tel:7148932106">Call (714) 893-2106</a>
        <a class="btn btn-o" href="/contact">Request online</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
